  {
    "row": 25,
    "rowsha": "2fEYK67hjsnFvYRo/av7f4a05bHC/6NzkKU7olxf/kE=",
    "originContent": "Are you beginning with Meteor? Do you want to get a sense of \"what is going on\" or even to optimize your Meteor app? This is the tool for you.",
    "translatedContent": "你刚开始使用 Meteor 吗？想了解“发生了什么”甚至优化你的 Meteor 应用吗？这款工具正适合你。"
  },
